==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unbarricade
<hw>Un*bar`ri*cade"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>barricade</ets>.]</ety> <def>To unbolt; to unbar;
to open.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>You shall not <qex>unbarricade</qex> the door.</q> <rj><qau>J.
Webster (1623).</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unbarricadoed</ent>⟦br⟧
